sequenceDiagram
    participant GG as genesis-generator
    participant GETH as geth
    participant LH as lighthouse
    participant LHV as lighthouse-validator

    Note over GG: Phase 1 - Genesis Generation
    GG->>GG: entrypoint.sh all
    GG->>GG: Generate genesis.json (EL)
    GG->>GG: Generate genesis.ssz (CL)
    GG->>GG: Generate config.yaml (CL)
    GG->>GG: python3 -m http.server 8000
    Note over GG: readinessProbe GET /metadata/genesis.json

    Note over GETH: Phase 2 - EL Init
    GETH->>GG: initContainer wget genesis.json (retry)
    GETH->>GETH: initContainer geth init
    GETH->>GETH: Start geth with JWT

    Note over LH: Phase 3 - CL Init
    LH->>GG: initContainer wget genesis.ssz + config.yaml (retry)
    LH->>LH: Create deposit_contract_block.txt
    LH->>LH: Start lighthouse beacon_node
    LH->>GETH: Engine API connection (JWT)
    Note over LH,GETH: el_offline false

    Note over LHV: Phase 4 - Validator Init
    LHV->>GG: initContainer wget genesis.ssz + config.yaml
    LHV->>LHV: lighthouse account validator recover
    Note over LHV: BLS keys from same mnemonic
    LHV->>LHV: Start lighthouse validator_client
    LHV->>LH: Beacon API connection 5052
    Note over LHV,LH: Block production starts
